  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_33",
    "english": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen.",
    "japanese": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen.",
    "korean": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen.",
    "spanish": "Witch. A half-blood born between a male demon and a female human. She's a witch but also a swordsman who wields the legendary demonic sword, Vajrayaksha.\n\nShe runs a detective agency both in the human world and the demon realm. She's acquainted with powerful leaders in Ami-dahara who are amiable towards her, but there are quite a few who are hostile towards her.\n\nShe's highly reputed as the strongest swordsman among Amidahara's swordsmen."
  },
